| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4637 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 009ffbd8-d2e8-54f4-9c7b-6752fa47d316"
